                <note rend="inline" type="source">860d.01/47: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-12-06T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 6, 1919, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>6247. Please ascertain the views of the Foreign Office with regard to full
                    recognition of Government of Finland.</p>
                <p>It is considered desirable that if full recognition be accorded, it be determined
                    upon contemporaneously by the four principal associated governments.</p>
                <p>Repeat to Paris and Rome.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
